item.title: Requiem for a Dream - Radiohead "Last Flowers"
item.description:
Requiem for a Dream - Radiohead "Last Flowers"

www.vimeo.com/davidmilstein From the In Rainbows second disk, "Last Flowers," edited to the film Requiem for a Dream. Apologies for the low quality, this was done in 2008 before HD and all that, and YouTube won't replace the file like Vimeo...so here we are. Enjoy!
